1
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:10,280
[Am I dead?]

2
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:26,879
[Is this]

3
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:30,760
[the legendary]

4
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:32,439
[rotating lantern?]

5
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,480
[These are our memories.]

6
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:48,680
[Our memories have merged into one.]

7
00:01:51,439 --> 00:01:52,719
[So I am you,]

8
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,200
[yet not you.]

9
00:01:58,519 --> 00:02:00,359
[Though we belong to different eras,]

10
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,599
[the things that make us feel angry,]

11
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:05,239
[repressed,]

12
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:07,040
[and unjust]

13
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,199
are remarkably similar.

14
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,319
Actually, meeting you again

15
00:02:16,319 --> 00:02:17,280
has always been my wish.

16
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:19,319
Your wish?

17
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:22,280
I once believed

18
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,039
that fate was unchangeable,

19
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,840
set in stone.

20
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:29,280
But as I faced death that day,

21
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,599
in my final moments of consciousness,

22
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:34,439
I thought,

23
00:02:35,639 --> 00:02:36,719
if there's a next life,

24
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:39,360
I must be a woman

25
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:40,759
a woman not bound by anything,

26
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:44,520
fighting against those tyrants

27
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,479
who are selfish and hypocritical.

28
00:02:47,719 --> 00:02:48,400
I'm sorry.

29
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:49,719
I lost.

30
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,919
And me.

31
00:03:12,439 --> 00:03:14,120
It feels good to fight back.

32
00:03:40,599 --> 00:03:41,319
So,

33
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,159
our boss let us take a vacation

34
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,560
to protect us.

35
00:03:47,039 --> 00:03:48,680
Qin Yeren fled everywhere.

36
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,800
Xie Qiming secretly cast a net.

37
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:52,759
My lord thought there might be a hidden danger,

38
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,240
so he sent us away early

39
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,479
to a safe place.

40
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,439
Before they cast their net,

41
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:00,560
the fish all ran away,

42
00:04:00,919 --> 00:04:02,879
and it looked like we were unprepared.

43
00:04:03,439 --> 00:04:05,080
Why does my lord only tell you when he fights,

44
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,039
not me?

45
00:04:07,280 --> 00:04:08,759
I've long noticed that my lord is biased.

46
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:10,400
Look at yourself,

47
00:04:10,479 --> 00:04:12,039
the way you're jumping around now.

48
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:13,879
You should know the reason by now.

49
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,360
After this war,

50
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:19,759
Miss Jiang will become Li Feiyuan again.

51
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,519
Then,

52
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,680
we'll be busy.

53
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:48,800
Are you tired?

54
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:50,920
It doesn't matter.

55
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:52,920
I promised to accompany you all day.

56
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:55,480
I remember that on the Lantern Festival,

57
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:57,600
I sneaked out to see lanterns.

58
00:04:58,879 --> 00:05:00,199
You searched for me on the street

59
00:05:01,319 --> 00:05:02,240
all night.

60
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:06,600
There were so many people at that time

61
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:07,839
it was hard to move.

62
00:05:08,399 --> 00:05:09,879
I knew you were right behind me,

63
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,319
but you pretended not to find me

64
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:14,319
just to let me enjoy the lanterns.

65
00:05:16,759 --> 00:05:17,319
Zang Feng,

66
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,560
I want to fly a sky lantern.

67
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,399
You really don't make a wish?

68
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:39,800
My wish has already come true.

69
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,480
One more thing,

70
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,199
you have to promise me.

71
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:05,279
Okay,

72
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,879
protect Jiang Yue well from now on.

73
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:12,480
Don't worry.

74
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:14,680
She's very generous.

75
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,279
I wanted to leave directly,

76
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,480
but she offered to give her body to me,

77
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,600
insisting that I see you one more time.

78
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:37,120
I am the memory Jiang Yue sensed.

79
00:06:39,519 --> 00:06:41,360
Now that her memory is complete,

80
00:06:43,639 --> 00:06:44,759
I can leave.

81
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:46,959
Where are you going?

82
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,800
Anywhere I want to go.

83
00:06:51,279 --> 00:06:52,639
I can be a gust of wind,

84
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,360
or a bird.

85
00:07:03,279 --> 00:07:03,800
Zang Feng,

86
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,240
we may never meet again.

87
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:33,879
You can forget about me.

88
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:39,199
I won't.

89
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,040
Guess how many candies are here.

90
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:03,759
If you guess it right,

91
00:08:03,839 --> 00:08:04,680
all five candies are yours.

92
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,879
How old are you?

93
00:08:17,959 --> 00:08:19,360
If I'm much older than you,

94
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,480
do you mind?

95
00:08:22,079 --> 00:08:22,800
Mind what?

96
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:27,199
Mind me being your boyfriend?

97
00:08:31,839 --> 00:08:32,679
You mean

98
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:36,279
a friend of a friend of yours

99
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,480
wants to be my boyfriend?

100
00:08:38,720 --> 00:08:39,200
No.

101
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,200
It's me.

102
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:42,480
I like you.

103
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,200
I want to be your boyfriend.

104
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,919
Confession should have a sense of occasion, okay?

105
00:08:53,679 --> 00:08:54,720
You should prepare

106
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,320
a romantic place

107
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,120
and invite many people to witness our happiness.

108
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,240
There should be flowers, sea, and gifts.

109
00:09:02,440 --> 00:09:04,080
It can't be so casual.

110
00:09:04,639 --> 00:09:06,120
What you're talking about is a proposal.

111
00:09:09,679 --> 00:09:10,399
Right.

112
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,039
But

113
00:09:15,519 --> 00:09:17,480
will you mind my origin?

114
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:18,960
Don't you Wolf Clan

115
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:21,039
hate your enemy the most?

116
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,960
People can't choose their origin,

117
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:28,240
but they can choose

118
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,720
their future.

119
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:31,840
I'm willing to

120
00:09:32,840 --> 00:09:34,320
walk with you in the future.

121
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:38,159
Then you promise...

122
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:42,240
The Wolf Clan oath is unbreakable.

123
00:09:58,879 --> 00:09:59,840
Are you

124
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,559
serious?

125
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:09,000
Although my resume is not very rich,

126
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,080
I will be responsible

127
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:12,600
to be a good keeper.

128
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:15,080
We will take turns

129
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:16,000
to clean up.

130
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,399
We will take good care of this place

131
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:18,960
and keep it in good order.

132
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:24,440
I see.

133
00:10:25,679 --> 00:10:26,399
You agree?

134
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,399
Then we'll go to work.

135
00:10:32,279 --> 00:10:33,039
A Che, stay here.

136
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:35,120
Let's talk.

137
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,600
You go first.

138
00:10:44,759 --> 00:10:45,639
I intended

139
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:50,200
to let you take over all my properties.

140
00:10:53,000 --> 00:10:53,559
Why?

141
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,279
I've been living here

142
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,840
for so many years.

143
00:10:57,480 --> 00:10:58,240
If I don't get older,

144
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,480
people will think I'm a monster.

145
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,080
So you're going to

146
00:11:14,919 --> 00:11:16,279
leave me here alone again?

147
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,799
With someone you love by your side,

148
00:11:26,679 --> 00:11:27,759
you won't feel lonely.

149
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:32,240
This is the home I've built

150
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:33,440
over the years.

151
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,200
Only by leaving it to you

152
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:38,000
can I be at peace.

153
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:47,519
Okay.

154
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:50,639
Go.

155
00:12:18,759 --> 00:12:19,639
Still studying me?

156
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,840
This is the note my mom left.

157
00:12:24,879 --> 00:12:26,480
Now I can finally remember

158
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:29,480
the time she used to camp with me in the forest

159
00:12:29,919 --> 00:12:30,960
and observe animals.

160
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,600
Those adventures

161
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,919
seem like yesterday.

162
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,039
Now we

163
00:12:41,679 --> 00:12:43,000
are about to start a new adventure.

164
00:12:45,879 --> 00:12:46,679
Where are we going?

165
00:12:47,879 --> 00:12:50,320
You prepared so many thick clothes yesterday.

166
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:52,360
Could it be that

167
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:57,679
the legend of the snow wolf is true?

168
00:12:58,559 --> 00:12:59,519
They are

169
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:00,919
a family

170
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:04,039
living in the snowy forests of the Scandinavian Mountains

171
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:07,840
at the border between Sweden and Norway.

172
00:13:09,360 --> 00:13:10,080
I'm not afraid of the cold.

173
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:11,720
You should wear more.

174
00:13:14,240 --> 00:13:14,840
But

175
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,799
I'm not one of them.

176
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,799
Will they welcome me to visit?

177
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,879
I will tell them

178
00:13:21,759 --> 00:13:22,799
that she is my wife.

179
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:28,960
So,

180
00:13:37,679 --> 00:13:38,639
will you marry me?

181
00:13:44,159 --> 00:13:45,159
Good.

182
00:13:45,559 --> 00:13:47,120
You cunning little dog.

183
00:13:53,720 --> 00:13:54,320
I do.

184
00:14:05,159 --> 00:14:06,840
This is a meteorite from Sirius.

185
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,879
It's priceless.

186
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:10,840
So?

187
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,240
So,

188
00:14:14,399 --> 00:14:15,080
it means

189
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,799
you're also my priceless treasure.

190
00:14:23,559 --> 00:14:24,799
You're so cheesy.

191
00:14:31,159 --> 00:14:32,759
Today, we're here

192
00:14:33,759 --> 00:14:35,639
to witness the wedding of Mr. Lu Zhiyu

193
00:14:36,440 --> 00:14:38,320
and Ms. Jiang Yue.

194
00:14:39,039 --> 00:14:39,799
Mr. Lu Zhiyu,

195
00:14:40,519 --> 00:14:42,879
will you take Ms. Jiang Yue

196
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,360
as your wife?

197
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:46,960
I do.

198
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,080
Ms. Jiang Yue,

199
00:14:49,759 --> 00:14:51,120
will you take Lu Zhiyu

200
00:14:51,399 --> 00:14:52,480
as your husband?

201
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:54,000
I do.

202
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:57,279
Please take the vows.

203
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:09,279
I will always respect your freedom,

204
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,159
support every choice you make,

205
00:15:12,559 --> 00:15:13,279
cherish you,

206
00:15:15,279 --> 00:15:16,000
and protect you.

207
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,320
I will share everything with you,

208
00:15:20,679 --> 00:15:22,240
through good times and bad,

209
00:15:23,399 --> 00:15:24,519
and always trust you,

210
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,080
without fear.

211
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,240
I will love you unconditionally

212
00:15:35,759 --> 00:15:36,519
forever.

213
00:15:37,559 --> 00:15:38,879
I will always be there for you,

214
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,240
until we grow old,

215
00:15:44,559 --> 00:15:45,519
throughout lifetimes,

216
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,120
faithful to the end.
